This file details each of the documents or files found in this repository, to aid finding the correct one swiftly.
If you build this tester. please show your gratitude for the time & effort put into this projiect, 
for your free use, by saying 'Hi' on the Photrio thread & also posting photos of your build.

https://www.photrio.com/forum/threads/build-a-shutter-tester-for-focal-plane-shutters-cheap-easy-it-works.197756/page-15

ARDUINO FOLDER:-

AVRDUDESS-2.14-setup.exe
 Executable file to install AVRDUDES, a program required to flash the Shutter Tester code to the Nano board. 
  (See document Arduino_Firmware_load)

Arduino IDE software load.pdf
This document details how to install the computer software to view results via the computer screen

Arduino Shutter Tester Operating Guide
  Description of how to use the Shutter Tester

Arduino Shutter Tester Parts.pdf
  List of parts required to make the Arduino version of the Shutter Tester. With links to & pictures of the parts

Arduino Shutter Tester hardware Build.pdf
  A guide of how to physically build the tester, with, pictures & examples of completed testers

Arduino Shutter Tester wiring diagram.pdf
  Schematic of wiring & photos of a completed tester

Arduino Shutter Tester firmware load.pdf
  A guide to getting the Shutter Timer code onto the Arduino Nano board.

Arduino_shuttertimer_x_x_x_ori.ino.hex
  The software to be loaded onto the Arduino Nano board.
  Note this is for the original sensors

Arduino_shuttertimer_x_x_x_new.ino.hex
  The software to be loaded onto the Arduino Nano board
  Note this is for the newer sensors and is the FW that should normally be used.

Arduino_shuttertimer_x_x_x.v_ini.hex beta  
  Pre-release beta version of firmware. For users to load find any bugs.
  Check in with the photrio forum before using this code

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

ESP32 FOLDER:-

1_ESP32_shutter_tester_parts.pdf
  A list of the parts required to makethe ESP32 version of the shutter tester. With links to and pictures of the parts.

2_ESP32_Hardware_Build.pdf
   A guide of how to physically build the tester, with, pictures & examples of completed testers

3_ESP32_wiring_guide.pdf
   Photos & guide of wiring.

4_ESP_32_Installing CP2102 or CH340 USB Driver.pdf
  Guide to installing CP2102 driver for ESP32 board

5_ESP32_Arduino_software_load.pdf
  This document details how to install the computer software to view results via the computer screen 

6_ESP32 Shutter Tester Firmware load.pdf
  A guide to getting the software onto the Arduino Nano board.

7_ESP32_Shutter_Tester_Operating_Guide.pdf
  Description of how to use the Shutter Tester

8_build a box.pdf
 Describes one method of marking out and cutting a project box

9_ESP32 Shutter Tester Film_Gate Sensor.pdf
 An atlertave method of mountning the semnsors. 

10_ESP32 Shutter Tester tft_schematic_x_x_x_x_full.pdf
 Schmenatic diagram showing connections - full version

10_ESP32 Shutter Tester tft_schematic_x_x_x_x_full_bb.pdf
 Schmenatic diagram showing connections - minimal version

CP210xUniversal_Windows_Driver.zip
 Windows driver for the ESP32 on-board USB interface.

Flash Download Tools.zip
  Compresssed folder containing 'Flash Download Tools', a program required to flash the Shutter Tester code to the ESP32 board. 
  (See document ESP32 Firmware load)

ESP_32_Shutter_Tester tft_schmatic_old_full.pdf
 Old hardware version, pre FW 3_0_9_0

ESP_32_Shutter_Tester tft_schmatic_old_minimal.pdf
 Old hardware version, pre FW 3_0_0_9

ESP_32_Firmware subfolder.
 Within here, you will find one or more folders with current and old firmware versions.

Each folder contains three files:-
esp32_shutterTester_x_x_x_x.ino.bootloader.bin
esp32_shutterTester_x_x_x_x.ino.partitions.bin
esp32_shutterTester_x_x_x_x.ino.bin

Additionally, files listed as 'beta' maybe shown. Refer to the Photrio thread before using these.

Active builders & users thread. If you start making the project, please say 'hi' here

https://www.photrio.com/forum/threads/build-a-shutter-tester-for-focal-plane-shutters-cheap-easy-it-works.197756/page-15


